{
  "name": "Partial Differential Equation Systems OGC Blocks",
  "abstract": "OGC Blocks implementation which uses the OGC standards SOSA, PROV and STAC combined to generate an interface for publishing the simulation results from a pytho-plankton and zoo-plankton interaction described by partial differential equations and numerically solved by using the Runge-Kutta method.\n",
